name: Vintage Camera 1.1
description:
A vintage Pentax camera without logo or branding marks, but with its leather textured body. Each illustration will be signed, numbered and printed on lovely cream 120 gsm paper.

The photo frame is not included in the purchase!

name: Eat Your Seasons
description:
A birthday calendar with 12 unique illustrations of the vegetable of the season. The vegetables are engaging in witty dialogue with each other and each vegetable also comes with an interesting fact.

To see more photos of the inside, click here: http://goodputty.com/#/eat-your-seasons/

Each calendar is specially packed and tied with colourful reusable kitchen rope. Have fun using it!

name: Spanish gentleman with red balloon
description:
He certainly didn't start out Spanish but he definitely ended up one. Perhaps he fell in love with the women and the music and decided to grow a Spanish Moustache.

Every order will be recreated by my very hand on the same thick brown recycled card. No prints sold here!

* Black picture frame not included.

options.name: To add words in the balloon, please contact me for possibilities.

name: The Girl With A Red Balloon
description:

name: The Green Fairy
description:
"The first stage is like ordinary drinking, the second when you begin to see monstrous and cruel things. But if you can persevere you will enter in upon the third stage where your see things that you want to see."

I am not Oscar Wilde, but he may have had a glimpse of my little green fairy sitting on a pebble in a dark lane outside his favourite cafe.

These notepads are printed on 80gsm paper, 160mm x 100mm and have 100 sheets. The poem on each sheet was written by my mother:

Beneath the moon and stars,
Where the Fairy Tale begins
Breezing through the clouds
hand in hand
Love freely shimmering bright,
True affection is where
the Fairy Tale lives
